*** linux common command , tmux , vi editor etc.

*** tmux
** install
sudo apt-get install tmux

** tmux prefix ctrl + b
c - create new window
d - detach this window
l - lately window
n - next window
p - previous window
w - check window number
window number - move to number
& - window close
, - rename

% - divide vertically
" - divide horizontally
q - check pane number
o - next pane
{ , } - control pane locate
direction key - change focus pane
alt + direction key - control pane size
space bar - pane layout


